227
00:17:13,125 --> 00:17:17,298
the photometric measurement 
that will allow to learn more

228
00:17:17,298 --> 00:17:18,895
about this object.

229
00:17:18,895 --> 00:17:22,562
Now the way this is going to function,
it is competitive.

230
00:17:22,562 --> 00:17:28,271
ESA will organize 
a time allocating committee.

